{
  "stem": "6052.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And said she was a [INAUDIBLE] of the Israelitische-- that she was a member of the Israelitische Gemeinde-- so was my mother-- and she had to wear also at that time the Judenstern, the Judenstern.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that she was living at that time in this Judenhaus, which was a ghetto of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this occurred at 1942 in January, and my grandmother in May [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She also was correctly assumed that because of her age and of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But what was even worse what I became aware how this happened and what this meant to be deported.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the most horrible act in a lifetime to occur to a family.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a night which was 17 below zero.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they arrived at Riga, after they were hit and injured and dreadfully treated.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they arrived at Riga, it was double-cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was 33 below zero.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a most horrible thing, as I learned from a description from one who survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- although there, they came from many cases, not only Leipzig.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was from many other places in Germany that the deportations took place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also to Riga and to other places, to Riga, and Riga is in Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And over there was a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I cannot call it differently-- perhaps they call it 'ghetto'-- with-- where 30,000 Jews died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some were rescued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some were helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And perhaps with the assistance of the people who-- some people who lived there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they could escape to, as described, to Danzig, which was a satellite of Poland at that time-- was independent later.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was also taken by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But at that time, they could make it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Or it was delivered.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am not sure what really happened with Danzig at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
